battle of the souls is a 2007 supernatural ugandan thriller directed by matt &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it featured in the 28th african film festival of verona ( italy ) . dubbed the ' first ' &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; feature film , it was also matt 's maiden film after returning home to kampala in 2005 from film school in amsterdam . he assembled a cast that made film history . it received 10 nominations at the 5th africa movie academy awards and eventually &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; the awards for best visual effect and best supporting actor .